Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I get my Quirk, I wanna be like him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that was true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're below the rejects!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Quirkless!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you even stand\Nin the same ring as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell can {\i1}you{\i0} do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that's what everyone thinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Izuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't have a Quirk,\Ncan I become a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can even someone without a Quirk be like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a Quirk...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit, goddammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It might've been because I don't have a Quirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm always made fun of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why... I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think saving people is super cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving people with a fearless smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be the greatest hero, like you...!
Comment: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:22.70,Alt,,0,0,0,,Texas Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for that bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsuki, aren't you\Nand Midoriya childhood friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You went a little overboard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his fault for getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that it's been\Nmy goal ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't know unless I try...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an idiot dreaming like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watching him pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we go to\Nthe arcade for a change of pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come, too, right, Katsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go to the\None in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of prey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get caught, it'll end up on my record!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An invisible cloak with a great Quirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You're deflating...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A fa— A fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so skinny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am All Might...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how the guys at the pool\Nare constantly flexing and posturing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might is fearless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He saves everyone with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the greatest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A fearless smile, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen me like this, young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...make sure you don't write\Nabout it online, even accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an injury I got from an\Nenemy's attack five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Half of my respiratory organs were destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I lost my whole stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become emaciated from\Nrepeated surgeries and the aftereffects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I can only work as a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...for about three hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that when you fought Toxic Chainsaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But a punk like that couldn't defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight was not made public to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked that it not be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save people with a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Symbol of Peace cannot be daunted by evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I smile to show the pressure of heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...and to trick the fear inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros are always risking their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot simply say, "You can\Nbecome a hero even without power."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to help others,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then you could also become a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're often teased because\Nthey get villains delivered to their doorstep,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but that is also a fine occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you also have to consider\Nwhat's realistic, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I need to quickly get this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What hero will go to the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot simply say, "You can\Nbecome a hero even without power."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A child was taken hostage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't grab hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Death Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let sewage like this swallow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You little—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With this Quirk and power,\NI can get revenge on that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, what's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he be a big-shot villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The rookie hero, Mt. Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait... I need there to be at least two lanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with explosions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to someone else for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my hands full fighting the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire truck's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sticky and hard to grab,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and a child with a strong\NQuirk is struggling against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, it's a minefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do anything\Nagainst this triple play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one who can take\Ncare of this at the scene right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is wait for\Nsomeone with a more suitable Quirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hold back the damage until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm sure someone will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for that child, but\Nhe'll just have to bear it a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had enough\Npower to blow that guy away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doesn't it look kinda bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too distracted by my time limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I made a mistake\Nlike this after admonishing that fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic...
Comment: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He still can't face reality, even though\Nhe's already a third year in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for you to think\Nseriously about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You also have to consider what's realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a top pro said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you\Nwere trying so desperately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You were averting your eyes,\Nnot looking at reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where the explosion earlier was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, does that mean\NI came out of habit without noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll just feel meaningless right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that guy here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it get away from All Might?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he drop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...then it's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't the heroes doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the villain caught a junior high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been like that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been like that for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they bear that suffocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd die after a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, wasn't that villain the one\NAll Might was chasing earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might? No way! He's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I saw him earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's All Might doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't catch that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is wait for a hero\Nwith a more suitable Quirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Help will arrive soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A hero... will soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Deku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I run out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Die in an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? What do I do at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Page 25!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs moved on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there were various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you even stand in the same ring as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.20,Alt,,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Unless I try...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:46.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,It's been my goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.70,Alt,,0,0,0,,He saves everyone with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked like you were asking for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll die in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he suicidal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I admonished you,\NI wasn't putting what I said into practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros are always risking their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Detroit Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's from the wind pressure just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An updraft developed and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He made... clouds...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With just his right fist,\Nhe changed the weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's All Might for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...heroes collected the scattered sludge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and safely delivered it to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, there's a limit to how rash you can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There was absolutely no reason\Nfor you to put yourself in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I got majorly scolded by the heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Kacchan was praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing toughness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And that Quirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're a pro,\Nplease come to my agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll definitely be an excellent sidekick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize to All Might...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he was still getting interviewed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try sending him a message\Non his website when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Deku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked you for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Quirkless failure playing without a full deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to make me owe you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn nerd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Toughness"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Kacchan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I accomplished anything,\Nor changed anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can think of a realistic future...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All Might?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You were surrounded by reporters until just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting away from them was a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am All Migh—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I come with thanks, a correction, and a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't been there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't told me about your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've turned into a guy\Nin a bodysuit who was all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I got in the way of your work...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I said all those impertinent\Nthings even though I'm Quirkless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because it was none other\Nthan the timid, Quirkless {\i1}you{\i0} at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I was able to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Top heroes have stories\Nabout them from their school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of their stories have one thing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bodies moved before\Nthey had a chance to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...I remembered my mother's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Izuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was true for you, too, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, what I wanted you to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The words I wanted to hear were...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...can become a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams can become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I forgot to mention that this is\Nthe story of how I became the greatest hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man, you are worthy to inherit my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Inherit your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my Quirk, One For All!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.55,0:24:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I can become a hero, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Your body can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Roaring Muscles"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Midoriya will get buff!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.70,0:24:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus Ultra!
